== Taariikdiisa ==
Mucaad wuxuu ku dhashay [[madiina]] (yasrib) wuxuu ka ahaa [[ansaar]] ree [[khazraj]], laf la yiraahdo [[banii jusham|banii salima]] ayuu ka sii ahaa, mucaad wuxuu islaamay asigoo jira 18 sano<ref name="أسد">[https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1110/page-5174 أسد الغابة في معرفة الصحابة - معاذ بن جبل] {{Whive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415103629/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1110/page-5174|date=15 أبريل 2017}} {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415103629/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1110/page-5174|date=15 أبريل 2017}}</ref>, wuxuuna xaadiray [[beca caqaba labaad]]

Markuu nabiga u soo haajiray [[madiina]] wuxuu walaaleeyay mucaad iyo [[Cabdulaahi bin mascuud|ibni mascuud]]<ref name="سعد2">[https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1099 الطبقات الكبرى لابن سعد - مُعَاذُ بْنُ جَبَلِ (2)] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415013849/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686/page-1099|date=15 أبريل 2017}}</ref>, waxa uu kala qeyb galy rasuulka scw [[Dagaalkii Beder|dagaalkii badar]] iyo dhamaan dagaalada kale <ref>ابن منظور، مختصر تاريخ دمشق، صفحة 368 369. بتصرّف

إقرأ المزيد على موضوع.كوم:</ref>

Markii la [[Furashada makka|furtay makka]] sanadkii 8aad hijiriga wuxuu Nabiga scw u xushay [[cataab bin useyd]] inuu tujiyo salaada, mucaadna wuxuuna faray inuu dadka baro [[Qur'aan|Qur'aanka]] oo u sharaxo mabaadi'da diinta, Markii uu waajibkaas gutay oo uu [[Medina|Madiina]] ku soo laabtay, waxa uu sii waday baridda [[Qur'aan|qur’aanka]] iyo cilmiga diinta, wuxuu la tukan jiray nabiga scw kadib  tolkiisa ree banii salima ayuu aadi jiray oo tujin jiray<ref>https://islamic-content.com/hadeeth/929</ref> waxaa dhacday mar inuu ka soo dacwooday nin cabanaya salaada oo dadka ku dheereen jiray, nabiga scw ayaa aad uga carooday waxa uu faray inuu fududeeyo salaada maadaama uu ku daba tukanayaan qof weyn, qof yar iyo mid dan leh <ref> https://www.alukah.net/sharia/0/149351/%D8%B4%D8%B1%D8%AD-%D8%AD%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%AB-%D8%A3%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%B9%D9%88%D8%AF-%22%D8%A5%D9%86-%D9%85%D9%86%D9%83%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%86%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%86%22/ </ref>

Sanadkii 9aad hijiriga nabiga scw ayaa u diray cariga [[yaman]] si uu dadka diinta ugu yeero, waxa uu siiyay dadrdaan oo ku dhahaayay; <blockquote> mucaadow waxaa u tagi doontaa qolo [[ahlu kitaab]] ah waxa ugu horeeya aa ugu yeereeso ha ahaado inay Alla waxidaan, hadeey kaa yeelaan ogeysii inuu Alla ku faral yeelay shan salaadood maalin kasta iyo habeen kasta, hadeey kaa yeelaan ogeysii inuu Alla ku faral yeelay sadaqo laga qaadaayo kuwooda taajiriinta ah laguna celinaayo kuwooda fuqarada ah, hadeey kaa iska jir xoolahooda wanaagsan kana dhowrso habaarka qofka dhibana ah uma dhaxeeyo asaga iyo Alla wax xijaab ah <ref> https://hadeethenc.com/ar/browse/hadith/3390 </ref></blockquote>

in mudo ah ayuu ka waday mucaad dacwad dhulka [[yaman]] <ref> https://hadeethenc.com/ar/browse/hadith/3390 </ref>
